  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bloxolotl is a cozy puzzle game all about cute block-shaped Axolotls and connecting them together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/c99cfc08b9c4e17675b0d83009582e4a.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Game features all varieties of Block-shaped Axolotls – Bloxolotls. You can wake them up and move them around. But they can only move in certain directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/a23b9b3f9ad76962f98ac47b37d9e950.poster.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=113 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/a23b9b3f9ad76962f98ac47b37d9e950.webm?t=1747736710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/a4a1ff1f5e80a5fcafc5e7252dba4173.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most of the Bloxolotl's have sticky sides. The Puzzles require you to connect them in a clever way. By doing that, you can combine their movement abilities. But be careful, connections can't be undone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/be13c39c126fa855da43b849a5d16705.poster.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=173 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/be13c39c126fa855da43b849a5d16705.webm?t=1747736710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/6ec50037aec495426cf45191b50487dd.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bloxolotls are hungry by nature. Every Puzzle asks you to feed them some fruit. Yummy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/6870eed5104667f727425d1a3b67766d.poster.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=123 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/6870eed5104667f727425d1a3b67766d.webm?t=1747736710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/5bb277859269e5068f07a1908e1b1442.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 50 Levels in four different zones with distinct mechanics.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bloxolotl is a cozy puzzle game all about cute block-shaped Axolotls and connecting them together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/c99cfc08b9c4e17675b0d83009582e4a.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Game features all varieties of Block-shaped Axolotls – Bloxolotls. You can wake them up and move them around. But they can only move in certain directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/a23b9b3f9ad76962f98ac47b37d9e950.poster.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=113 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/a23b9b3f9ad76962f98ac47b37d9e950.webm?t=1747736710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/a4a1ff1f5e80a5fcafc5e7252dba4173.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most of the Bloxolotl's have sticky sides. The Puzzles require you to connect them in a clever way. By doing that, you can combine their movement abilities. But be careful, connections can't be undone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/be13c39c126fa855da43b849a5d16705.poster.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=173 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/be13c39c126fa855da43b849a5d16705.webm?t=1747736710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/6ec50037aec495426cf45191b50487dd.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bloxolotls are hungry by nature. Every Puzzle asks you to feed them some fruit. Yummy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/6870eed5104667f727425d1a3b67766d.poster.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=123 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/6870eed5104667f727425d1a3b67766d.webm?t=1747736710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945940/extras/5bb277859269e5068f07a1908e1b1442.avif?t=1747736710\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 50 Levels in four different zones with distinct mechanics.</p>",
